Description: NVM with Node 24 LTS and Angular CLI for Technical Platform WSL
 This package installs NVM (Node Version Manager) and Node.js 24 LTS
 for all users. Angular CLI is pre-installed globally.
 NVM allows managing multiple Node.js versions.
